WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.040
My day in a life as a 25 year old trap wife.

00:00:02.041 --> 00:00:04.801
We started our morning activity with watercolors for Wind Week.

00:00:04.802 --> 00:00:08.121
Got myself a shower and then I went ahead and fixed stop our room.

00:00:08.122 --> 00:00:10.201
I really love opening the windows in the morning.

00:00:10.202 --> 00:00:12.961
Practice some piano which I am struggling with.

00:00:12.962 --> 00:00:14.961
And then this room just needed picked up.

00:00:14.962 --> 00:00:15.841
It was driving me nuts.

00:00:15.842 --> 00:00:19.001
My toddler now thinks it's funny to chase me around when I'm vacuuming.

00:00:19.002 --> 00:00:20.921
